OL,3,CSouth Africa is best value long-haul
OL,4,Choliday destination ` report
OL,6,FSouth Africa has regained its position
OL,7,Fas the best value long-haul holiday
OL,8,Fdestination for UK travellers,
OL,9,Faccording to a new report.
OL,11,FLocal price falls and the weakening of
OL,12,Fthe South African rand have brought
OL,13,Fcosts down for UK visitors by 12%
OL,14,Fsince autumn 2023, Post Office Travel
OL,15,FMoney said.
OL,17,FThis makes Cape Town the best value
OL,18,Fout of 32 resorts and cities analysed
OL,19,Fin the annual study for the first time
OL,20,Fsince 2018.
