OL,6,FTypical prices include #1.63 for a cup
OL,7,Fof filter coffee, #1.81 for a bottle
OL,8,Fof local beer, and #33.31 for a three-
OL,9,Fcourse evening meal for two with a
OL,10,Fbottle of house wine.
OL,12,FTokyo, Japan, was be the second best
OL,13,Fvalue long-haul destination, followed
OL,14,Fby Vietnam's Hoi An, which took top
OL,15,Fspot last year.
OL,17,FAt the other end of the scale, Sydney,
OL,18,FAustralia, was the most expensive,
OL,19,Fwith tourist staples costing nearly
OL,20,Fthree times more for UK visitors than
OL,21,Fin Cape Town.
